        "description": "Official Postman Collection for Huidu Payment Gateway.\n\n**Authentication:**\nStrictly header-based. Requests are signed using `MD5(JSON_Body + Secret_Key)`.\n\n**Setup:**\n1. Select the environment or use Collection Variables.\n2. Set `base_url` (e.g., `http://localhost:3000` or `https://your-domain.com`).\n3. Set `merchant_uuid` and `merchant_key` from your dashboard.\n\nThe Pre-request Script automatically calculates the `x-signature` header.",
